<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīlōluṇḍagubra<unclear>hma</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>ṇḍanāyakapadārtthāyattuṇḍai yurvvaranu vā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> muṁddu dānavasēncekrapratāpaṁbunanu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ana<unclear>ghuṁ</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>kuna kātanikiṁ ggulakāntayaina yaṁggana Eṟiyāṁbakunu madanakalpuṇḍu vuṭṭeṁ jaturtthavaṁśavarddhanu ṇḍanavadyu ṇḍuttamavadānyuṇḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>ṇḍu vīralakṣmīkini ganiyagu daṇḍanāyakaśikhāmaṇi gāmana suprasiddhuṁḍai [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>1*] dhīrōdāttuṇḍugāmināyakuṇḍu bhaktiṁ jēsi nityasthitini bhū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rikhyāti śakakṣitīśa samamulu bhūśailadiksaṁkhyayaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dārāmaṁbulakella nāyakamunānatyuṇnatiṁ bolcu dākṣārāmaṁbuna nilpē dī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pamu sadākhaṇḍaprabhābhāsigānu [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>2*]svasti śakavarṣa 1071 ṇḍagu nēṇṭi viṣumusaṁkrānti nimittamuna śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku daṇḍa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nāyaka kāmināyaku peṭṭina Akhaṇḍavartti lōhadaṇḍu di 1 ṇṭiki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyiṁccuvārugā bōlu nalupuru
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁ būṇṭagā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> larāśi bhīmanabōyini Aḍapunaṁ gētabhōladāmani vasamunaṁ beṭṭina InupaEḍlu 50 ṇṭiki nitya
<lb n="9" break="no"/><unclear>paḍi</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <unclear>likhi</unclear>ṁta sūrācāryya<unclear>ṇaḥ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
